## Release Process

* Check/Update NEWS
* Increase version in configure.ac (see semver.org)
* Commit, merge to stable and tag (see branching[1])
$ ./bootstrap.sh && make distcheck

[1]: See do a release in
     http://www.draketo.de/branching-strategy#action-maintainer

